Revision history for Perl extension Linux::WireGuard:

0.03
- Fix compatibility with old Test::More versions.

0.02 Mon 18 Jul 2022
- Rename Wireguard -> WireGuard.
- Make `endpoint` undef if there is no endpoint for a given peer.
- Added add_device() and del_device().
- Added tests.
- Fix repo information in Makefile.PL.

0.01 Sat 16 Jul 2022
- Initial release
